{"word":"G4154 - πνέω - pnéō - pneh'-o - Blow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pnéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pneh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Blow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அடி, வீசு"},{"paragraph":"to breathe, to blow"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary word; to <i>breathe</i> hard, that is, <i>breeze</i>: - blow. Compare <a href=\"#/G5594 - ψύχω - psýchō - psoo'-kho/5594\">G5594</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1606/1606\">G1606</a>, <a href=\"#/G2315/2315\">G2315</a>, <a href=\"#/G4151/4151\">G4151</a>, <a href=\"#/G4152/4152\">G4152</a>, <a href=\"#/G4153/4153\">G4153</a>, <a href=\"#/G4154/4154\">G4154</a>"}]}